<blockquote className="">{`
`}
<h5 className="">{`Conveying meaning to assistive technologies`}</h5>
{`
`}
<p className="">{`Using color to add meaning only provides a visual indication,
which will not be conveyed to users of assistive technologies – such as screen readers.
Ensure that information denoted by the color is either obvious from
the content itself (e.g. the visible text), or is included through alternative means,
such as additional text hidden with the `}
<code className="">{`.sr-only`}</code>
{` class.`}</p>
{`
`}</blockquote>
{`
`}
<p className="">{`Assign `}
<code className="">{`sm`}</code>
{`, `}
<code className="">{`md`}</code>
{`, `}
<code className="">{`lg`}</code>
{` or `}
<code className="">{`xl`}</code>
{` to `}
<code className="">{`responsive`}</code>
{` property,
making the table scroll horizontally at each `}
<code className="">{`max-width`}</code>
{` breakpoint of up to (but not including)
576px, 768px, 992px, and 1120px, respectively.`}</p>
{`
`}
<blockquote className="">{`
`}
<p className="">{`Note that since browsers do not currently support `}
<a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/mediaqueries-4/#range-context" className="">{`range context queries`}</a>
{`,
we work around the limitations of `}
<a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/mediaqueries-4/#mq-min-max" className="">{`min- and max- prefixes`}</a>
{` and viewports with fractional widths
(which can occur under certain conditions on high-dpi devices, for instance)
by using values with higher precision for these comparisons.`}</p>
{`
`}</blockquote>
{`
`}
<h2 className="">{`Responsive tables`}</h2>
{`
`}
<p className="">{`Responsive tables allow tables to be scrolled horizontally with ease.`}</p>
{`
`}
<blockquote className="">{`
`}
<h5 className="">{`Vertical clipping/truncation`}</h5>
{`
`}
<p className="">{`Responsive tables make use of `}
<code className="">{`overflow-y: hidden`}</code>
{`, which clips off any content that goes beyond the bottom or top edges of the table.
In particular, this can clip off dropdown menus and other third-party widgets.`}</p>
{`
`}</blockquote>
{`
`}
<h3 className="">{`Always responsive`}</h3>
{`
`}
<p className=""><code className="">{`<Table />`}</code>
{` is responsive & horizontally scrollable defaultly.`}</p>
